# `content.config.ts`

- Collections **`posts`**, **`teamMember`**, **`legalPage`** only; folder `base` paths must stay aligned with `apps/web/src/content/*`.
- Changing collection names breaks `getCollection("posts")` in **`Search.astro`** — update that import and any loaders.
- Image shape is **`{ url: string; alt?: string }`** only; do not switch to Astro `image()` without migrating consumers and markdown frontmatter.
